    <h3 itemprop="headline">Bear caught on camera perched atop New Mexico utility pole before reportedly suffering fatal electrocution</h3>
    <p itemprop="text">
      Viral video shows a bear perched atop a utility pole along a rural New Mexico highway, panting and struggling to keep its balance on the precarious perch.
      <a itemprop="url" href="/us/2026/07/23/bear-caught-camera-perched-atop-new-mexico-utility-pole-before-reportedly-suffering-fatal-electrocution/"  >(Fox News)</a>
